It is rare that I have to ask for a res as Malefic is my personal res &quot;bitch&quot; (/grin Malefic).  But on occasion I get his ranger killed and then have to find him one.  In these cases I always look for my cleric friends online.  I really do hate to ask strangers for res's.  If it's a friend not close, I provide the transportation to and from (benefit of being a druid).  If no friends on, then I will look close but I usually hold out for a friend logging on.<br>
